{"tid":44813,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[砌女]壽屋FA FAG模型討論區","createTime":"2016-12-18T14:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T11:40:38.000Z","uid":67343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b18b6f9ccc60d211f17a3bceda5c1fd99d703c7f","tid":44813,"uid":67343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"身邊無咩人玩壽屋模型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個post取下暖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q&amp;A</span><br />\n<br />\nQ:咩係FA?<br />\nA:FA全名Frame Arms 是壽屋推出的原創模型。FA系列的最大特徵是使用全系列通用的素體，以在素體上裝上外甲而完成各種機械人。因為素體和外甲都是使用3mm接口，令FA系列擁有極高的互換性和擴展性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dne5z13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdne5z13.jpg&h=0e750b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88y3OqZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88y3OqZ.jpg&h=d4af22d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:咁咩係FAG?<br />\nA:FAG全名Frame Arms Girl 是上述Frame Arms系列的擬人化模型。將美少女和機械結合的機娘模型。以可愛的造型及不差於FA的互換性取得玩家的芳心<del>(特別是武裝神姬難民)</del><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Q32eU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Q32eU3.jpg&h=3d8c9722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:香港邊到有?<br />\nA:本人見過有售的店鋪如下:<br />\n福利模型<br />\n元朗榮興<br />\n現時點2F<br />\n玩巨帝國<br />\n皆旺21樓<br />\n觀塘模型谷<br />\n(歡迎補充)"},{"pid":"30b519045e38f148c6baf96f8cd171b29cac83cb","tid":44813,"uid":67343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"補返官網先<br />\nFA官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kotobukiya.co.jp/product-title/%E3%83%95%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A0%E3%82%A2%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A0%E3%82%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotobukiya.co.jp%2Fproduct-title%2F%25E3%2583%2595%25E3%2583%25AC%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25A0%25E3%2582%25A2%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25A0%25E3%2582%25BA%2F&d=myV3ArmkQETIy5dlh0Xiu2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=5112a1ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kotobukiya.co.jp/product-title/%E3%83%95%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A0%E3%82%A2%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A0%E3%82%BA/</a><br />\nFAG官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kotobukiya.co.jp/product-title/framearmsgirl/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotobukiya.co.jp%2Fproduct-title%2Fframearmsgirl%2F&d=myV3ArmkQETIy5dlh0Xiu2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=63d638e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kotobukiya.co.jp/product-title/framearmsgirl/</a>"},{"pid":"22387e06ee0111860a110dc196c160dae35a9a2c","tid":44813,"uid":67343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf94ef0da32f271776f9f74a833ab9d8a432bda","tid":44813,"uid":67343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e6b5a00bf0aa9a4598da1eddc5029e320b2d45","tid":44813,"uid":67343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"拋磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j8gga6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj8gga6a.jpg&h=0c44af27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07v63Op.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07v63Op.jpg&h=a175da2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81uDX4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81uDX4m.jpg&h=5f56a471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/234242_45fd01027434ce2f609076e0459a16d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F234242_45fd